ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce et d'industrie du Sud-Ouest de Montréal (Quebec) ** CHANGE OF BOUNDARIES **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE ET D'INDUSTRIE DU SUD-OUEST DE MONTRÉAL in Quebec TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the municipalities of LaSalle and Verdun to the boroughs of Sud-Ouest, LaSalle and Verdun.
